r levels.  Max lvl chars should not be able to cap out all stats at 255 with buffs (are we all gods running around? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Stats should be extremely powerful with end game items offering +2 - +3 to 1 or 2 stats at the most.  Any +hp/mana items should be balanced against their relative value per stat.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uvaclavromanov.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vaclav Romanov</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_bluespot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/26/02 1:30:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23487.topic&index=5>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: EQ2 - Rebirth of the Rogue class</span><hr size=1> Good point...<br><br>/hopes...<br><br>I do enjoy cleric'ing in EQ1... but a real 'Thief'-style rogue is very very close to my heart...<br><br>BTW, on a non-EQ related note:<br><br>www.ionstorm.com/THIEF3/ was a link I found the other day on RPGDOT.com I'm already happy as hell about that... (link might be a little off) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ubronusblackblade.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bronus Blackblade</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>R